    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/9e154cae2202586df13654506e732ecb.poster.avif?t=1754640291\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/9e154cae2202586df13654506e732ecb.webm?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/9e154cae2202586df13654506e732ecb.mp4?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Kommander: Fascination of Evil is a strategic turn-based RPG that places you at the helm of powerful armies battling across vast and immersive landscapes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in large-scale, tactical warfare, commanding knights, orcs, trolls, mages, and dragons, where every move counts, and strategy is key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/09f8a6d482b99af433caa2ca4ea84fa0.poster.avif?t=1754640291\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/09f8a6d482b99af433caa2ca4ea84fa0.webm?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/09f8a6d482b99af433caa2ca4ea84fa0.mp4?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Marcus III, a noble knight renowned for his victories in tournaments and loved by his people. Lead him and his army as they embark on a quest to reclaim Imperial lands, crush enemy forces, and restore peace to the realm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to unravel the secrets hidden within the ancient forests of the Empire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/ebe3685f1e9f52c01d9bde13226c9b9b.poster.avif?t=1754640291\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/ebe3685f1e9f52c01d9bde13226c9b9b.webm?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251470/extras/ebe3685f1e9f52c01d9bde13226c9b9b.mp4?t=1754640291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your power step by step as you conquer enemy territories, collect powerful items, and grow stronger with each battle. Hire new units from the inn, deploy them strategically on the battlefield, and unleash devastating attacks to overwhelm your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Are you ready to command fearlessly and claim victory for the Empire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developer Note:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is an artifact originally developed in 2009  by a small independent team that uses all the potential and limitations of flash technology. We apologize for any technical problems or inconveniences you may encounter while playing the game, and hope that despite these limitations, you can still enjoy the experience as it was originally intended to be played on the AgeofGames portal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
